  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This real-world study aimed at 1. exploring the relationships of traditional Chinese medicine
      (TCM) syndrome and internal diseases, 2. investigating the relationships of TCM treatment and
      internal diseases, and 3. creating medical machine intelligence to help internal physician in
      clinical practice. Big data methods and artificial intelligence algorithms are used to assess
      the associations based on electronic case files of patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
